      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i've been walking this trail for forever, just through this thick, grey fog. it's so exhausting. i finally reached the edge of the woods today and there's just... nothing left. the path just stops at this cliff and there's no way forward. it's like the world just ended here.",
